Label: MHC1
Comment: In humans, the HLAs corresponding to MHC class I are HLA-A, HLA-B, and HLA-C. https://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/MHC_class_I

Label: MHC2
Comment: In humans, the MHC class II protein complex is encoded by the human leukocyte antigen gene complex (HLA). HLAs corresponding to MHC class II are HLA-DP, HLA-DM, HLA-DOA, HLA-DOB, HLA-DQ, and HLA-DR. https://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/MHC_class_II
